Class FileData

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileData

  • public class FileData
extends Object
    Helper class to store the election data from a file: FileData is an abstraction that contains the information from the election data files. Files are expected to be in the format Election year and election type, name1, name2, name 3 region1,count11,count12,count13 region2,count21,count22,count23 ...
